        </div>
    </div>
</div>
                        
                        <p>It is easy to be critical of Cutcliffe and his staff for failing to build on last year’s momentum, but they managed to sustain it despite the graduation of a game-changing quarterback. While this season should not be considered a success, give the man some more time with players he recruited. I expect a bowl game before Renfree graduates­, and Duke’s chances have never been better. </p>

